  "description": "This dataset contains electrophysiological recordings from distributed intracortical silicon electrodes (DISC) implanted in rat somatosensory cortex during whisker stimulation. Anesthetized rats received air puff stimulation to individual whiskers while neural activity was recorded.",
  "methods_description": "DISC microelectrode arrays were surgically implanted in rat somatosensory cortex. During anesthesia, whisker stimulation was delivered using an air puffer, with task identifiers corresponding to the stimulated whisker.",
